The network of examination centres will operate under the auspices of the Pushkin Institute of Russian Language, the University of Friendship of Peoples, Moscow State University, St. Petersburg State University and other Russian higher education institutions.
Immigrants will be able to submit to the tests in all cities, right now in Russia are open more than 160 centers of this type.
