And after 10 hours in the newborns there was a total atrophy of the instincts.
The chicks did not react to light or sound.
And the unfortunate thing was that after four days they were just dying.
“And twice we managed to get the chicks born, but then we left it because it was impossible to work there with them,” comments Vladimir Sychev on the failure of the experiment with the chicks in space.
