The CIA, in collaboration with the Canadian authorities, managed to get them out of Iran, for which a covert story helped an extravagant point: they came out with Canadian passports, as members of the film crew that examined the location in the country for the shooting of a science fiction overproduction.
Combination of genres
The plan drawn up by "exfiltration" expert Toni Mendez required Hollywood's collaboration.
