A bus full of whites singing songs in a language of blacks; such recognition not only brings with it an excellent atmosphere and a lot of joy, but it has also managed to tear away a couple of tears from some angry border soldier.
The trip always takes them to Esitjeni, where the singers visit the sponsored children.
